snippet.title: Pixel Cafe - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming-of-age story about family, relationships, coffee and life in the big city. Immerse yourself in the perfect blend of an arcade-style time manager and visual novel, exploring dual storylines and a beautifully crafted pixel art world in Pixel Cafe.

Wishlist Pixel Cafe on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2409360/Pixel_Cafe/

Coming in fall 2023 to Steam, Nintendo Switch, Xbox and Playstation

Trailer edited by: Kacper Pitała
